def miss_table(data):
    missings = pd.DataFrame(data.isna().mean()*100, columns = ['% miss'])
    missings['# miss'] = pd.DataFrame(data.isna().sum())
    display (missings.style.background_gradient('coolwarm'))

def des_var(data):
    for i in list(data):
        if (data[i].dtypes!='object') and (data[i].nunique() > 20):
             display (data[i].describe())
        else: 
            display (data[i].value_counts())
        print ('------------------------------')
        print (' ')

In [15]:
def pie_cat(df, category, name, value, legend): 
    temp_df = df.pivot_table(index = category, values = value, aggfunc = 'count')
    temp_df.plot.pie(y=value, figsize=(10, 10), autopct="%.1f%%")
    plt.legend(legend)
    plt.title(' {}    '.format(name))
    plt.show()

def bar_cat(category, name, legend): 
    temd_df_3 = gym.pivot_table(index = category, values = 'id', columns = 'Churn', aggfunc = 'count')
    temd_df_3[0] = temd_df_3[0]/temd_df_3[0].sum()
    temd_df_3[1] = temd_df_3[1]/temd_df_3[1].sum()
    temd_df_3 = temd_df_3.transpose()
    temd_df_3 = temd_df_3.drop(0, axis = 1)
    temd_df_3 = temd_df_3.transpose()
    ax = sns.barplot(data=temd_df_3)
    plt.legend(legend)
    plt.title(' {}       '.format(legend))
    ax.set_xlabel('   Vs.  ', fontsize=15)
    ax.set_ylabel('', fontsize=15)
    plt.show()

def bar_cat_mean(value, name): 
    temd_df_4 = gym.pivot_table(index = 'Churn', values = value, aggfunc = 'mean')  
    temd_df_4 = temd_df_4.reset_index(level=0)
    ax = sns.barplot(data=temd_df_4, x = 'Churn', y = value)
    #plt.legend(legend)
    plt.title('   {}     '.format(name))
    ax.set_xlabel('   Vs.  ', fontsize=15)
    ax.set_ylabel(' ', fontsize=15)
    plt.show()

Обучение моделей и оценка их метрик¶

In [34]:
def print_all_metrics(y_true, y_pred, y_proba, title=' '):
    print(title)
    print('\tAccuracy: {:.2f}'.format(accuracy_score(y_true, y_pred)))
    print('\tPrecision: {:.2f}'.format(precision_score(y_true, y_pred)))
    print('\tRecall: {:.2f}'.format(recall_score(y_true, y_pred)))
    print('\tF1: {:.2f}'.format(f1_score(y_true, y_pred)))
    print('\tROC_AUC: {:.2f}'.format(roc_auc_score(y_true, y_proba)))
